 r‚Üêlevel Help Cmd;ref;‚éïTRAP;path
 r‚Üê''
 :Select level
 :Case 0
     :Select ‚éïC Cmd
     :Case ‚éïC'AddTatinDependencies'
         r,‚Üê‚äÇ'Add one or more Tatin packages as dependencies'
         r,‚Üê‚äÇ']Cider.AddTatinDependency [packages] [projectpath] -development -target='
     :Case ‚éïC'AddNuGetDependencies'
         r,‚Üê‚äÇ'Add one or more NuGet packages as dependencies'
         r,‚Üê‚äÇ']Cider.AddNuGetDependencies [packages] [projectpath] -target='
     :Case ‚éïC'CloseProject'
         r,‚Üê‚äÇ'Break the Link between one or more project spaces and their associated files on disk'
         r,‚Üê‚äÇ']Cider.CloseProject [<namespace-name>|alias-name] -all -fast'
     :Case ‚éïC'Config'
         r,‚Üê‚äÇ'Print the contents of Cider''s global config file, and optionally edit it'
         r,‚Üê‚äÇ']Cider.Config -edit'
     :Case ‚éïC'CreateProject'
         r,‚Üê‚äÇ'Convert the given folder into a project'
         r,‚Üê‚äÇ']Cider.CreateProject <folder> [<project-namespace>] -alias= -acceptConfig -noEdit -batch -ignoreUserExec'
     :Case ‚éïC'Help'
         r,‚Üê‚äÇ'Put the HTML help files on display'
         r,‚Üê‚äÇ']Cider.Help'
     :Case ‚éïC'LinkConfig'
         r,‚Üê‚äÇ'Print the contents of any .linkconfig file, or edit or delete it'
         r,‚Üê‚äÇ']Cider.LinkConfig -edit -delete'
     :Case ‚éïC'HowToMakeNewVersion'
         r,‚Üê‚äÇ'Print the project''s specific statements to the session that create a new version ("Make")'
     :Case ‚éïC'HowToRunTests'
         r,‚Üê‚äÇ'Print the project''s specific statements to the session that run the test suite'
     :Case ‚éïC'ListAliases'
         r,‚Üê‚äÇ'List all defined aliases with their folders'
         r,‚Üê‚äÇ']Cider.ListAliases -prune -edit -batch -scan='
     :Case ‚éïC'ListNuGetDependencies'
         r,‚Üê‚äÇ'List all NuGet dependencies'
         r,‚Üê‚äÇ']Cider.ListNuGetDependencies [projectpath]'
     :Case ‚éïC'ListOpenProjects'
         r,‚Üê‚äÇ'List all open projects'
         r,‚Üê‚äÇ']Cider.ListOpenProjects -verbose'
     :Case ‚éïC'ListTatinDependencies'
         r,‚Üê‚äÇ'List all Tatin dependencies'
         r,‚Üê‚äÇ']Cider.ListTatinDependencies [projectpath] -full -latest'
     :Case ‚éïC'OpenProject'
         r,‚Üê‚äÇ'Load all source files into the WS and keep them linked by default along with additonal actions'
         r,‚Üê‚äÇ']Cider.OpenProject [folder|alias] -projectSpace= -parent= -alias= -suppressInit -import -noPkgLoad -ignoreUserExec -watch=ns|dir|both -verbose -batch'
     :Case ‚éïC'ProjectConfig'
         r,‚Üê‚äÇ'Display the config file of a project'
         r,‚Üê‚äÇ']Cider.ProjectConfig [path] -edit'
     :Case ‚éïC'UpdateCider'
         r,‚Üê‚äÇ'Attempt to update the currently running version of Cider'
         r,‚Üê‚äÇ']Cider.UpdateCider'
     :Case ‚éïC'Version'
         r,‚Üê‚äÇ'Return name, version number and version date as a three-element vector'
         r,‚Üê‚äÇ']Cider.Version'
     :EndSelect
     :If ~(‚äÇ‚éïC Cmd)‚àä‚éïC'Version' 'Help'
         r,‚Üê''(']Cider.',Cmd,' -?? ‚çù Enter this for more information ')
     :EndIf
 :Case 1
     ref‚Üêhelp.level_1
     path‚Üê(‚çïref),'.',‚éïC Cmd  ‚çù for editing the vars
     ('Unkown: ',Cmd)Assert 2=ref.‚éïNC Cmd
     r‚Üêref‚çéCmd
 :Case 2
     :If 0<help.‚éïNC'level_2'
         ref‚Üêhelp.level_2
         path‚Üê(‚çïref),'.',Cmd  ‚çù for editing the vars
     :AndIf 2=ref.‚éïNC Cmd
         r‚Üêref‚çéCmd
     :Else
         r,‚Üê‚äÇ'There is no additional help available'
     :EndIf
 :EndSelect
